  "texts": [
    "How we engage with advanced machines in the future depends not only on the voices that determine how we bring forth aspects of our own systemic embedding, but also on the voices that determine the actions and perceptions of the people who shape intelligent machines.",
    "not have been possible without the exceptional support of my supervisor, Stephen Cowley.",
    "I am incredibly grateful for the constant intense intellectual exchange that has helped me to develop my ideas.",
    "I would also like to express my deep gratitude to the Ph.D. committee -Sarah Bro Trasmundi, Paul Cobley, and Hannele Dufva-who provided invaluable feedback on the first version of this work.",
    "I thank them for their valuable and constructive suggestions to improve my ideas about human presencing."
  ]
}